  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The necessity of orthopedic implant removal is under intense discussion and even if it is
      performed as an elective procedure, the risk of complications is present.

      Aim of the study is to identify parameters responsible for an increased risk of early
      post-operative complications after elective aseptic orthopedic implant removal.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
